 website, viewed May 20, 2021)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:13.555Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220348/", "image_url": [], "index": 10, "language": ["english"], "location": ["salt lake", "utah", "salt lake city", "united states"], "number": ["701514958", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2768-4016", "2021220348", "online resource"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Salt Lake Democrat", "Evening Democrat"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "salt lake evening democrat (salt lake city, utah) 1885-1887 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 47.46009, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD F821", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "salt lake city (utah)", "united states", "salt lake", "utah", "salt lake city"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:02:05.412Z", "title": "Salt Lake evening Democrat", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021220348/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220567/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1902", "dates": ["[1902 TO 1902]"], "description": ["Weekly Print began with vol. I, No. 1 (February 11, 1902); ceased with vol. I, No. 42 (November 25, 1902). Vol. I, No. 1 (February 11, 1902); title from caption (Chronicling America's website, viewed November 9, 2021). Vol. I, No. 42 (November 25, 1902) (Chronicling America's website, viewed November 9, 2021). Inter-mountain farmer 2770-999X (DLC) 2021220568 (OCoLC)778032255"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:17.248Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021220567/", "image_url": [], "index": 11, "language": ["english"], "location": ["salt lake", "utah", "salt lake city", "united states"], "number": ["2770-9949", "online r